{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-modules-jsx","path":"/modules/additional-rails","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"additionalrails\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#additionalrails\" aria-label=\"additionalrails permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AdditionalRails</h1>\n<p>AdditionalRails is an extension for the <a href=\"https://github.com/Terasology/Rails\">Rails</a> module which adds many new carts, rails, and other features.</p>\n<h2 id=\"features\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#features\" aria-label=\"features permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Features</h2>\n<p>Here is a brief list of the features which this module adds:</p>\n<h3 id=\"carts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#carts\" aria-label=\"carts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Carts</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Activable Cart Example: Prints a message to the logger when is passes over an Activator Rail</li>\n<li>Explosive Cart: Explodes when it passes over an Activator Rail</li>\n<li>Harvesting Cart: Harvests plants from the <a href=\"https://github.com/Terasology/SimpleFarming\">SimpleFarming</a> module</li>\n<li>Planting Cart: Plants plants from the <a href=\"https://github.com/Terasology/SimpleFarming\">SimpleFarming</a> module</li>\n<li>Hoover Cart: Picks up items around it when fueled by torches</li>\n<li>Track Layer Cart: Lays tracks from its inventory as it moves</li>\n<li>Tunnel Bore Cart: Lays tracks and digs a 3x3 tunnel as it moves</li>\n<li>Cargo Cart: Holds a lot of items, but gets heavier and moves slower the more it is holding</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"rails\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rails\" aria-label=\"rails permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Rails</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Booster Rail: Boosts carts that pass over it</li>\n<li>One-way Booster Rail: Boosts carts in only one direction</li>\n<li>Activator Rail: Activates carts that pass over it</li>\n<li>Friction Rail: Has much more friction than other rails</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"switches\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#switches\" aria-label=\"switches permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Switches</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Lever Switch: Controls the rail juntion direction, controlled by 'use target' action (usually 'E' key)</li>\n<li>Signal Switch: Same as the Lever Switch, but controlled by a signal from the <a href=\"https://github.com/Terasology/Signalling\">Signalling</a> module instead of the player</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"screenshots\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#screenshots\" aria-label=\"screenshots permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Screenshots</h2>\n<p><img src=\"screenshots/railtypes.png\" alt=\"Rail Types\"></p>\n<p><em>Booster Rail, One-way Booster Rail, Activator Rail, and Friction Rail</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshots/expcart.png\" alt=\"Explosive Cart\"></p>\n<p><em>Results of an explosive cart</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshots/tunnel.png\" alt=\"Tunnel Bore\"></p>\n<p><em>Tunnel dug by a Tunnel Bore Cart</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshots/switch.png\" alt=\"Lever Switch\"></p>\n<p><em>Lever Switch in action</em></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"AdditionalRails AdditionalRails is an extension for the Rails module which adds many new carts, rails, and other features. Features Here isâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"AdditionalRails","cover":{"publicURL":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/cover.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/9e1f0/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/8dfb2/cover.jpg 480w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/2f986/cover.jpg 960w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/9e1f0/cover.jpg 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/3fa69/cover.webp 480w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/986c9/cover.webp 960w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/34dc0/cover.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}]},"width":1920,"height":1000}}},"date":null,"tags":["Library","Asset"]},"fields":{"slug":"/additional-rails","date":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/additional-rails"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1865044719"]}